title: Camtrack 2.4

*****************************************

Please seed if you like this application!

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

CamTrack lets you add video effects, cool animations and photo sharing to any webcam software or video chat application, It olso complements the webcam driver of your camera. It works with most USB webcams and is compatible with virtually all available video chat applications, such as Skype, Trillian pro, Camfrog, Eyeball Chat, iSpQ, iVisit, SightSpeed, MSN Messenger, Yahoo Messenger, ICUII and others. CamTrack is very easy to use and requires no configuration whatsoever.

You can find more animations for Camtrack on this website: http://digitalpeers.com/webcam-animations.php (You need to have Camtrack installed).
